class atom.organic_scoring.organic_queue.organic_queue.OrganicQueue(max_size=10000)[source]#

Bases: OrganicQueueBase

Basic organic queue, implemented as a list.

add(sample)[source]#

Add the sample to the queue

sample()[source]#

Randomly pop the sample from the queue, if the queue is empty return None.

Return type:

Any

property size: int#

atom.organic_scoring.organic_queue.organic_queue_base module#

class atom.organic_scoring.organic_queue.organic_queue_base.OrganicQueueBase[source]#

Bases: ABC

Base organic queue.

The following methods must be implemented:

  • add: Add the sample to the queue;

  • sample: Pop the sample from the queue;

  • size: Return the size of the queue.
